snippet.title: Evercade Mega Cat Studios 'Collection 1' Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
More info: https://evercade.co.uk/mega-cat-studios-collection-1-cartridge/

The ‘Mega Cat Studios’ Collection 1 cartridge brings 10 original ‘retro style’ games to the Evercade, including fan favourites ‘Log Jammers’ and ‘Coffee Crisis’!! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case.

Games list: 

- Multidude
- Super Painter
- Coffee Crisis
- Little Medusa
- Tänzer
- Old Towers
- Creepy Brawlers
- Almost Hero
- Log Jammers
- Justice Duel
